Effective 11/6/2025

10-7-88.

Municipalities to approve, protect certain protection areas.

A municipality shall comply with the following provisions of Title 17, Chapter 81, Agriculture, Industrial, and Critical Infrastructure Materials, the same as if the municipality were a county:

(1)Section 17-81-101, Definitions;

(2)Part 2, Proposal and Approval of Protection Area;

(3)Part 3, Protection of Land in a Protection Area;

(4)Part 4, Vested Mining Use; and

(5)Part 5, Open Land and Working Agricultural Land Use.

Enacted by Chapter 14, 2025 Special Session 1
